# TypeScript + Tailwind

## Layout

- `src/app/` — routes, layouts, global styles
- `src/components/` — UI
- `src/lib/` — data access, utilities, env
- `src/types/` — shared types

## TypeScript

- Explicit types for props, MongoDB documents, and serialized shapes.
- `interface` for objects; `type` for unions.
- `import type` when values are not needed.
- Validate external input at boundaries (`env.ts`, search queries).

## Tailwind v4

- Theme in `src/app/globals.css` (`@import "tailwindcss"`, `@theme inline`).
- Palette: `bg-zinc-950`, `text-zinc-100`, accents `text-amber-400`.
- Responsive breakpoints: `sm:`, `md:`, `lg:`.
- Fonts via `next/font` in `layout.tsx` (`--font-geist-sans`).

## Quality

- Follow `eslint-config-next`; semantic HTML with accessible contrast.
- Reuse existing helpers before adding abstractions.
